你講be water就啱，be water係唔係見乜就衝，冇策略，唔就情況轉變而變？<br />
<br />
&ldquo;I said empty your mind. Be formless, shapeless, like water. Now you put water into a cup, it becomes the cup. You put water into a bottle, it becomes the bottle. You put it in a teapot, it becomes the teapot. Now water can flow or it can crash. Be water, my friend.&rdquo;
